      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "大鬼上，众鬼卒同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00002",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "我乃六殿阎君麾下大鬼是也。今有刘氏青提，作恶多端，将她打在滑油山前受罪。众鬼卒，将刘氏青提押上来！",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00003",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众鬼卒同允。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00004",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "黑暗暗雾沉沉一阵昏暗，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00005",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘青提上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00006",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "回龙",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "一步来到鬼门关。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00007",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "鬼哥，唤我何事？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00008",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小鬼"
      ],
      "text": "长官唤你。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00009",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "哦，长官唤我。老身今年——",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00010",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "五十整，悔不该吃斋我又开五荤。转面来我便把长官一问，你唤我难人所为何情？",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00011",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "长官唤我何事？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00012",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "只因你在阳世之间作恶多端，阎君大怒，将你打在滑油山前受罪！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00013",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "鬼哥若是将我放回，从此改过就是。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00014",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "改过改过，难免你的心头之火。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00015",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "长官，此路难行，行个方便罢。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00016",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "难行也要行。诸鬼卒拉着走！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00017",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众鬼卒同允。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00018",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "苦呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00019",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "刘青提未起身珠泪伤惨，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00020",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众鬼卒同喝。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00021",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄快三眼",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "想起了当年事好不心烦。自幼儿吃长斋一心向善，十八岁进夫门配结良缘。遭不幸老员外黄泉命染，生一子无踪影绝了香烟。因此上心愤恨天地埋怨，在中年饮酒开荤、打僧骂道、改变心田。",
      "text_length": 84
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00022",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众鬼卒"
      ],
      "text": "走呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00023",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "何立他用言语苦苦相劝，到如今铁树开花方有见天。悔不该在佛堂发下誓愿，从此后破了杀戒、开了五荤、不信神佛、咒骂青天。",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00024",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众鬼卒同喝。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00025",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "阎罗王差五鬼白昼活现，才将我三魂七魄拉在阴间。看起来这时节后悔已晚，叹人生如泡如影，如幻如梦，果然有报应循环。",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00026",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众鬼卒"
      ],
      "text": "走呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00027",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘青提"
      ],
      "text": "在阴间见了些无情鬼判，在阴间见了些剑树刀山；在阴间见了些剥皮把草嵌，在阴间见了些堆捣磨研。行善的到阴间依旧行善，只见在走金桥，过银桥，左金童，右玉女，黄幡宝盖金罗伞，他好不威严！可怜我做恶的有谁怜念，到如今项带长枷、身背铁链，一步一打、一打一扑，获罪于天。",
      "text_length": 128
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00028",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众鬼卒同喝。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01003013_e00029",
      "play_id": "01003013",
      "scene_id": "01003013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
